OL,3,COfcom fines Royal Mail #10.5m for post
OL,4,Cmissing delivery targets
OL,6,FRegulator Ofcom has fined Royal Mail
OL,7,F#10.5 million for missing its post
OL,8,Fdelivery targets in the 2023-2024
OL,9,Ffinancial year.
OL,11,FThe fine is the second in two years,
OL,12,Fafter the watchdog also gave Royal
OL,13,FMail a #5.6 million penalty in
OL,14,FNovember 2023.
OL,16,FRoyal Mail said just under three-
OL,17,Fquarters of first class post was
OL,18,Fdelivered on time during the period,
OL,19,Fwell short of its 93% target.
