OL,4,Cmissing delivery targets
OL,6,FAnd 92.7% of second class post was
OL,7,Fdelivered on time, below its 98.5%
OL,8,Ftarget, it said.
OL,10,FIan Strawhorne, Ofcom director of
OL,11,Fenforcement, said: "With millions of
OL,12,Fletters arriving late, far too many
OL,13,Fpeople aren't getting what they pay
OL,14,Ffor when they buy a stamp.
OL,16,F"Royal Mail's poor service is now
OL,17,Feroding public trust in one of the
OL,18,FUK's oldest institutions.
OL,20,F"This is the second time we've fined
OL,21,Fthe company since the pandemic.
