OL,6,FBut they added that its one-price-goes-
OL,7,Fanywhere so-called universal service
OL,8,Fobligation needs "urgent reform", as
OL,9,Fit does not meet modern customers'
OL,10,Fneeds.
OL,12,FThe universal service currently
OL,13,Frequires Royal Mail to deliver letters
OL,14,Fsix days a week and parcels five days
OL,15,Fa week, but is under review.
OL,17,FThe fine comes as Czech billionaire
OL,18,FDaniel Kretinsky closes in on a deal
OL,19,Fto buy Royal Mail from current owner
OL,20,FInternational Distribution Services.
