OL,6,FDaniel Kretinsky's EP Group agreed to
OL,7,Fbuy IDS earlier this year, but is
OL,8,Fbelieved to have agreed to several
OL,9,Fconcessions to gain approval.
OL,11,FHe had already guaranteed to maintain
OL,12,Fthe universal service.
OL,14,FMr Kretinsky has also pledged not to
OL,15,Fraid the group's pension surplus, and
OL,16,Fkeep the brand name and Royal Mail's
OL,17,FUK tax residency and headquarters.
OL,19,FThere was also an agreement to respect
OL,20,Funion demand for no compulsory
OL,21,Fredundancies until 2025.
